    <summaries>
      <summary>
        <versionCode>00</versionCode>
        <actionDate>2017-06-07</actionDate>
        <actionDesc>Introduced in Senate</actionDesc>
        <updateDate>2018-05-18T15:55:10Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><strong>Home Mortgage Disclosure Adjustment Act</strong></p> <p>This&nbsp;bill&nbsp;amends the Home Mortgage Disclosure Act&nbsp;of 1975 to&nbsp;exempt a depository institution&nbsp;from certain records and disclosure&nbsp;requirements related to the itemization of loan data: (1) with respect to closed-end mortgage loans, if the depository institution originated fewer than 500 such loans in each of the two preceding years; and (2) with respect to open-end lines of credit, if the depository institution originated fewer than 500 such lines of credit in each of the two preceding years.</p> ]]></text>
      </summary>
    </summaries>
